('ONET-HEALTH_EDUCATION_SPECIALISTS', 'source_onet_health_education_specialists', 'Health Education Specialists', 'Health Education Specialists is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Provide and manage health education programs that help individuals, families, and their communities maximize and maintain healthy lifestyles. Use data to identify community needs prior to planning, implementing, monitoring, and evaluating programs designed to encourage healthy lifestyles, policies, and environments. May link health systems, health providers, insurers, and patients to address individual and population health needs. May serve as resource to assist individuals, other health professionals, or the community, and may administer fiscal resources for health education programs.', ARRAY['Behavioral Health Educator','BLS Instructor (Basic Life Support Instructor)','Breastfeeding Educator','Breastfeeding Peer Counselor','Certified Breastfeeding Educator (CBE)','Certified Diabetes Educator','Certified Health Education Specialist','Certified Lactation Counselor (CLC)','Certified Lactation Educator','Clinical Educator','Clinical Instructor','Clinical Nurse Educator','Clinical Trial Educator','Community Educator','Community Health Consultant','Community Health Education Coordinator','Community Health Educator','Community Health Worker (CHW)','CPR and First Aid Instructor (Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation and First Aid Instructor)','CPR Instructor (Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation Instructor)','Diabetes Educator','Early Breastfeeding Care Specialist','Education Coordinator','Education Specialist','Educator','Fitness Coach','Health Coach','Health Education Coordinator','Health Education Specialist','Health Educator','Health Promotion Specialist','Health Screener','Healthcare Educator','Healthcare Specialist','Instructor','Lactation Consultant','Lactation Specialist','Lamaze International Breastfeeding Support Sp